  "title": "Laundry Supervisor (Sign on reward)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage the overall daily operations of the linens section</li>\n  <li>Ensure quality controls are in place for all linens processes</li>\n  <li>Assigns and instructs the team on work to be performed</li>\n  <li>Provides training to the laundry team</li>\n  <li>Assigns schedules and duties to laundry staff as per business needs</li>\n  <li>Assists in the recruitment and selection of laundry personnel</li>\n  <li>Responsible for maintaining cleanliness of the linen area</li>\n  <li>Ensure employee observance of safety practices</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum PSLE qualification or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience; candidates with operational backgrounds from other industries are welcome to apply</li>\n  <li>Independent staff with strong leadership skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Receive a $500 Sign-On Reward!</strong><br>\n<em>Stay with us for 12 months to qualify. Terms and conditions apply.</em></p>\n<p><br></p>",
